{"tid":1679644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑政府利用警察正在企圖慢性毒殺市民","createTime":"2019-10-28T10:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T10:05:04.000Z","uid":118922,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9421d8370836b6262ce218b3f35dd739698df5a3","tid":1679644,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"首先，警察每星期都用催淚彈去驅散人群，不過就算無人都好，佢地都會照放<br />\n<br />\n但無論係有毒(可能含有催淚水劑)嘅顏色水定催淚彈，警察都無宣佈成份，亦無教過市民應如何處理<br />\n<br />\n而被噴射過嘅街道，其實都有化學殘留，但最近竟然加上蒙面法，唔比市民戴口罩，只要見到市民戴，警方就截查，如果話唔係想毒殺我地啲小市民係啲咩?<br />\n<br />\n另外，最近更經常射入商店內，周街咁射，我覺得做法相當唔可取<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqtUSmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqtUSmZ.jpg&h=4cdc085e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"776c6119ce812851a8afc3fbfd93391c9b20b75d","tid":1679644,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3gbRGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3gbRGC.jpg&h=94dd7b77&s={SIZE}\" />老豆搵仔：新疆單野俾譚仔搞到沉晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676450</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4dd733ff10b92904088011efcdd88ea98c64fe9a","tid":1679644,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"upup"},{"pid":"fd11da6b33c237511a7160024696ae7bfca34fcf","tid":1679644,"uid":188176,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"先黎係水<br />\n而家係空氣<br />\n之後大陸黎既食物好大機會加料<br />\n睇路"},{"pid":"793c82303cbb95256af362b8ba51072fd90f4ea4","tid":1679644,"uid":5523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqtUSmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqtUSmZ.jpg&h=4cdc085e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8054b22aa0cf53ab7e9bdfe733516255ae25f21e","tid":1679644,"uid":2